node.text: @hypefoods: For the first installment of the new 'Blended' series — a food-focused offshoot of How To showcasing delicious fusions— HYPEBEAST recently visited @pokeburriphilly, where restaurant manager Jessy showed us how an “everything” sushi donut is made.

node.text:
@hypeart: @sothebys is auctioning one of the original 11 copies of the US constitution this November. The record is “one of the most rare and coveted historical documents that has ever come to auction" and is expected to fetch around $15 million to $20 million USD. Learn more via the link in bio.⁠
Photo: Ed Jones/Getty Images

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @crocs has officially revealed plans to hit $5 billion USD in sales by 2026, while simultaneously committing to sustainability and to achieving a net-zero goal by 2030. Hit the link in bio to find out more about their plans.⁠ ⁠
Photo: Boston Globe/Getty Images

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HYPEBEAST A NEW LIFE SIZE GUNDAM STATUE IS COMING TO JAPAN'.

node.text:
#hypeAF: West Japan is set to receive its first 1:1 life-size Gundam statue next year. Mitsui Shopping Park Lalaport Fukuoka is scheduled to open in the city’s Hakata Ward and the concept which features ample shops, restaurants and an outdoor promenade is also slated to be the home of the new RX-93 Nu Gundam. The Mobile Suit is from 1988’s 'Char’s Counterattack,' the first original anime film of the franchise, and measures at a height of approximately 65.6 ft. The plaza is set to open in Spring 2022.⁠
Photo: Mitsui Shopping Park

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub: This incredibly rare @porsche 959 Komfort has headed to auction. The German classic boasts a “Wine Red Metallic” paint job that was produced under the Porsche Exclusive division known as the “Special Wishes” program. Some of the highlights include a color-matching interior, heated seats, and a 2.8-liter twin-turbocharged flat-six engine capable of 444 BHP. Hit the link in bio for more info.⁠⁠
Photo: @rmsothebys

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: On our latest installment of 'Sole Mates,' we caught up with Whitaker Group founder @james.whitner to discuss the process of creating the @thesocialstatus x Nike Dunk, using product as a vessel for communication, and more. Hit the link in bio for the full feature.⁠⁠
Photo: Social Status⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021 tagging @thesocialstatus, @james.whitner, and @hypebeastkicks. May be an image of 1 person, footwear and text that says 'CHAF TAT SOTE M JAMES WHITNER VAT MATES HYPEBEAST'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says 'Originally we were thinking Dunk Low or Dunk High. As we continued to unravel the story though, we saw how strong it was and decided we wanted something unique that would live with it. There are always going to be tons of different Dunk colorways, so we aimed to have something uniquely ours, something that spoke to our stories and experiences.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says '" Youth culture these days goes from the sneakers up, but the generation come from was about getting fly from head to toe. Sneakers accessorize dope clothes really well, and think they're the perfect way to complete any outfit.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021. May be an image of saddle-stitched leather, footwear and text that says '" It's always about social currency. When you mature, you start to realize that the items you wear provide social currency for you. That search for social currency sticks with you throughout your life. Ingredients: Nike Sportswear, Social Status, MilkyTPU w Gel YY Velvet, Diffuse Microbial Textile Lining, Tyvek Label,'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says '" When we started toying with the concept of "Free Lunch," we were thinking about what was important to a lunch. What was static, what was always there. We realized that the "free lunch" food menu is different day to day, but the drinks are always the same. We keyed in on that, and it gave us a canvas to start working on. SELL BY. FALL T 2021 D'.
Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, footwear and text that says 'Through sneakers we WILL change the world. STAT'.

node.text:
@hypeart: @joakimojanen has unveiled an eccentric set of sculptures for the new children's hospital at Östra Sjukhuset in Gothenburg, Sweden. The project has been six years in the making and features the Swedish artist’s signature humanoid characters as they invite spectators to interact across the grounds.⁠⁠⁠
Photo: Joakim Ojanen

@hypebeastkicks: @asapnast recently teased a newly surfaced @nst2lab x @reebok Zig Kinetica II. The shoe features a red upper that is accessorized with suede overlays and warped lines. NST2 branding can be seen on the heel tabs while the grippy sole is made with Vibram rubber for ample traction. Stay tuned for official release details.⁠⁠

@hypebeastwatches: Renowned accessories designer @judithleiberny has teamed up with @timex to rework two iconic watches in @swarovski crystals. Taking on the Q Timex and Timex T80, Leiber’s brand hand-applied over 900 Swarovski crystals to each timepiece. Find both editions online now with prices ranging from $1,000 to $1,200 USD.⁠⁠

Details include Swooshes in arrow-like silhouettes, ball-and-wings logos in vibrant yellow, orange and teal hues, and toe boxes with the word “Familia” on the right foot and “SiEMPRE” on the left’s tongue tab. Stay tuned for release details from @nike.⁠⁠

The off-roader boasts a Ford Windsor 438ci V8 engine capable of 1000 HP paired with a Gearstar Supermatic80 transmission, while 4×4 racing suspension and active 4-wheel steering making for the perfect "Blood Gulch" daily. Hit the link in bio for the full video build.⁠⁠

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: For Fall/Winter 2021, @gucci has introduced a new Ultrapace R made from transparent rubber, allowing for an updated display of the technical details. Towards the rear of the one-piece upper is a heel cup adorned with “GG” and Ultrapace R branding. Additional branding is also found on the wire dial closure system and clear rubber sole unit. The daring offering is now available from Gucci’s website and boutiques worldwide, for $890 USD.⁠⁠
Photo: Gucci

node.text:
@hypebeaststyle: ACRONYM, the brainchild of @erlsn.acr continues to deliver high-quality technical wares for Fall/Winter 2021. Throughout the monochromatic collection, highlights like the J29-LP Modular Blazer, J38-LP coat, and P38-DS Cargo Pant are seen constructed of top-of-the-line Loro Piana and Schoeller fabrics. In addition to a signature cyberpunk aesthetic, pieces boast functional details like Gravity Pockets, removable JacketSlings, and more. Hit the link in bio to learn more.⁠⁠
Photo: ACRONYM
